data.description: Welcome to 601 S Stewart Street.  Located at the heart of Azle, it offers quick access to Main Street's bustling shopping district, a tranquil park, and the local library.This spacious residence showcases three bedrooms, one bathroom, and a generous 1,637 square feet of living space.  Recent improvements have revitalised this home, including new kitchen countertops, modern shelving, an eye-catching backsplash, a state-of-the-art central HVAC system, an updated bathroom with stylish flooring and vanity, fresh carpeting on the lower level, and meticulously detailed trim work. Stainless steel appliances grace the kitchen, while the foundation has been expertly leveled, the floor plan artfully revamped, and both floors and kitchen cabinets carefully restored. Easy access to Hwy 199 & Hwy 730 and situated in the Highly sought after Axle ISD!
